Hello People 
Welcome to my railway reservation project repository . 
This project is solely made using C++ .  I used OOPs concept , file handling , Object writing and reading into/from the files . 
Some good features in our system are :
 1). New User signUp and Login Features also Forgot Password Features. 
 2). You can get list of trains from your boarding station to destination .
 3). Book Tickets .
 4). Make payment.
 5). Get pnr and Watch your ticket
 6). Give Feedback
 7). Register your greivances
 
I hope that you may like our project 
If you think improvements can be done then please share your valuable feedback.

            Thanks
            
            
            
